---
description: Export CF or CFE result for the current ITL branch
agent: code
---

Use this command only from an active `itldev/*` development branch worktree.

Run the helper directly from the current project directory:

If the agent shell tool supports `timeout_ms`, run this lifecycle command with `timeout_ms >= 3900000` by default so the outer shell outlives the 3600-second Designer limit; if that limit is configured higher, raise the outer timeout too. Do not use `120000 ms` or other short defaults because the helper may launch 1C Designer/Enterprise operations.

```powershell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\.agents\skills\1c-workflow\scripts\run-itl-command.ps1 -- -Action export-dev-branch-result
```

If the JSON summary has `confirmationRequired=true`, ask the developer for explicit confirmation before continuing. For confirmed unverified export, rerun the same compact command with `-AllowUnverifiedResult`. If `VERIFICATION_POLICY=block`, do not ask for an override; run `/itl-check` first. For other failures, read only the last 80 lines of `logPath`.
